
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Code Ninjas Dashboard</title>
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/icons/bootstrap-icons.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      --cn-blue: #358ebc;
      --cn-blue-dark: #1e6a94;
      --cn-blue-light: #e8f4fb;
      --cn-black: #1a1a1a;
      --cn-dark: #231f20;
      --cn-gray: #f5f6f8;
      --cn-gray2: #eaecf0;
      --cn-border: #dde1e7;
      --cn-text: #1a1a1a;
      --cn-muted: #6b7280;
      --cn-white: #ffffff;
    }
    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif; }

    .wrap { display:flex; min-height:100vh; background: var(--cn-gray); }

    .sidebar {
      width: 240px;
      background: var(--cn-dark);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: white;
      position: fixed;
      z-index: 1000;
    }
    .main { flex: 1; padding: 24px 28px; margin-left: 240px; overflow-y: auto; }

    .nav-link { color: #99aabb; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 4px 10px; text-decoration: none; display: block; font-size: 14px; transition: all 0.2s; }
    .nav-link:hover, .nav-link.active { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: white; }
    .nav-link.active { background: var(--cn-blue); }

  .topbar { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 22px; }
  .topbar h1 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--cn-black); }
  .topbar p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--cn-muted); margin-top: 3px; }
  .date-badge {
    background: var(--cn-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--cn-border);
    border-radius: 7px;
    padding: 7px 13px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--cn-muted);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .stat-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 22px; }
  .stat-card {
    background: var(--cn-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--cn-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 15px 16px;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--cn-blue);
  }
  .stat-card.accent-black { border-top-color: var(--cn-dark); }
  .stat-card.accent-teal { border-top-color: #2a9d8f; }
  .stat-card.accent-amber { border-top-color: #e09f00; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; color: var(--cn-muted); margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .stat-value { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--cn-black); }
  .stat-sub { font-size: 11px; color: var(--cn-muted); margin-top: 3px; }

  .section-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 4px; }
  .section-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: var(--cn-muted); }
  .section-line { flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--cn-border); }

  .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 20px; }

  .card {
    background: var(--cn-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--cn-border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 9px;
  }
  .card:hover { border-color: var(--cn-blue); box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(53,142,188,0.12); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  .card-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; }
  .card-icon {
    width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 18px;
  }
  .icon-blue { background: var(--cn-blue-light); color: var(--cn-blue); }
  .icon-dark { background: #f0f0f2; color: var(--cn-dark); }
  .icon-teal { background: #e6f6f4; color: #1a7a72; }
  .icon-amber { background: #fef9e7; color: #9a6e00; }

  .card-badge {
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
    padding: 3px 7px; border-radius: 4px;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.4px;
  }
  .badge-action { background: #e8f4fb; color: var(--cn-blue-dark); }
  .badge-data { background: #f0f0f2; color: #444; }
  .badge-log { background: #fef9e7; color: #9a6e00; }
  .badge-event { background: #e6f6f4; color: #1a7a72; }

  .card h3 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--cn-black); }
  .card p { font-size: 11.5px; color: var(--cn-muted); line-height: 1.5; }
  .card-arrow { font-size: 12px; color: #ccc; transition: color 0.15s; }
  .card:hover .card-arrow { color: var(--cn-blue); }

  .boss-card {
    background: var(--cn-dark);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    color: white;
  }
  .boss-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 13px; }
  .boss-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; }
  .boss-live { font-size: 10px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 4px; background: rgba(53,142,188,0.25); color: #80ccf0; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
  .hp-label { font-size: 11px; color: #8899aa; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .hp-bar-bg { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 4px; height: 7px; overflow: hidden; }
  .hp-bar { height: 7px; border-radius: 4px; background: var(--cn-blue); width: 62%; }
  .hp-text { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 11px; color: #8899aa; margin-top: 6px; }
</style>

<div class="wrap">
  <aside class="sidebar">
    <div class="p-4 text-center border-bottom border-secondary border-opacity-25 bg-white">
      <img src="/img/cn_logo.png" height="30" alt="Code Ninjas">
    </div>

    <div class="mt-4">
      <a href="/admin" class="nav-link active"><i class="bi bi-speedometer2 me-2"></i> Dashboard Home</a>
      <a href="/admin/dashboard-editor" class="nav-link"><i class="bi bi-pencil-square me-2"></i> Edit Ninja Dashboard</a>
      <a href="/admin/ninjabucks-editor" class="nav-link"><i class="bi bi-currency-dollar me-2"></i> Edit Ninja Bucks</a>
      <a href="/ninjabucks" class="nav-link"><i class="bi bi-coin me-2"></i> Ninja Bucks</a>
      <a href="/" target="_blank" class="nav-link"><i class="bi bi-eye-fill me-2"></i> View Ninja Dashboard</a>
      <a href="/logout" class="nav-link mt-4 text-danger"><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right me-2"></i> Logout</a>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <main class="main">
    <div class="topbar">
      <div>
        <h1>Sensei Dashboard</h1>
        <p>Track your ninjas' progress, rewards, and events</p>
      </div>
      <div class="date-badge" id="date-badge">Loading...</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats Hidden for now -->
    <div class="stat-row" style="display: none;">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-label">Active Ninjas</div>
        <div class="stat-value">48</div>
        <div class="stat-sub">Checked in today</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card accent-amber">
        <div class="stat-label">NinjaBucks Today</div>
        <div class="stat-value">1,240</div>
        <div class="stat-sub">Awarded this session</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card accent-teal">
        <div class="stat-label">Belt Advancements</div>
        <div class="stat-value">3</div>
        <div class="stat-sub">This week</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card accent-black">
        <div class="stat-label">Boss HP Remaining</div>
        <div class="stat-value">62%</div>
        <div class="stat-sub">Today's event</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-header"><div class="section-title">Ninja Dashboard</div><div class="section-line"></div></div>
    <div class="grid">
      <a href="/admin/dashboard-editor" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-top">
            <div class="card-icon icon-teal"><i class="bi bi-display"></i></div>
            <span class="card-badge badge-event">Public</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Edit Ninja Dashboard</h3>
          <p>Update activities, events, and Ninja of the Month for the lobby display.</p>
          <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/admin/ninjabucks-editor" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-top">
            <div class="card-icon icon-blue"><i class="bi bi-currency-dollar"></i></div>
            <span class="card-badge badge-action">Config</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Edit Ninja Bucks</h3>
          <p>Configure Google Spreadsheet integration and sync ninja leaderboard data.</p>
          <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/admin/shop-editor" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-top">
            <div class="card-icon icon-teal"><i class="bi bi-cart4"></i></div>
            <span class="card-badge badge-event">Public</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Edit Ninja Shop</h3>
          <p>Manage items, prices, and categories available in the Ninja Shop.</p>
          <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-top">
            <div class="card-icon icon-amber"><i class="bi bi-eye-fill"></i></div>
            <span class="card-badge badge-log">View</span>
          </div>
          <h3>View Ninja Dashboard</h3>
          <p>Open the kid-friendly dashboard in a new tab to see current changes.</p>
          <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="section-header"><div class="section-title">Actions</div><div class="section-line"></div></div>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card opacity-75">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-icon icon-blue"><i class="bi bi-person-plus-fill"></i></div>
          <span class="card-badge badge-secondary">NON-FUNCTIONAL</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Add Ninja</h3>
        <p>Register a new ninja and initialize their starting profile.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card opacity-75">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-icon icon-blue"><i class="bi bi-sliders"></i></div>
          <span class="card-badge badge-secondary">NON-FUNCTIONAL</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Buttons / Controls</h3>
        <p>Quick-action macros to award NinjaBucks or trigger events.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card opacity-75">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-icon icon-blue"><i class="bi bi-graph-up-arrow"></i></div>
          <span class="card-badge badge-secondary">NON-FUNCTIONAL</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Update Progress</h3>
        <p>Log belt tests, rank advancements, and curriculum milestones.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-header"><div class="section-title">Database</div><div class="section-line"></div></div>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card opacity-75">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-icon icon-dark"><i class="bi bi-database-fill"></i></div>
          <span class="card-badge badge-secondary">NON-FUNCTIONAL</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Master Data</h3>
        <p>All member stats, history, and metadata in one place.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card opacity-75">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-icon icon-dark"><i class="bi bi-grid-3x3-gap-fill"></i></div>
          <span class="card-badge badge-secondary">NON-FUNCTIONAL</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Progress Matrix</h3>
        <p>Visual overview of all ninjas' current belt and degree status.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
      </div>
      <a href="/ninjabucks" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit;">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-top">
            <div class="card-icon icon-dark"><i class="bi bi-journal-text"></i></div>
            <span class="card-badge badge-data">Public</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Ninja Bucks</h3>
          <p>View the full searchable/sortable Ninja Bucks leaderboard.</p>
          <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="section-header"><div class="section-title">Logs & Events</div><div class="section-line"></div></div>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card opacity-75">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-icon icon-amber"><i class="bi bi-clock-history"></i></div>
          <span class="card-badge badge-secondary">NON-FUNCTIONAL</span>
        </div>
        <h3>NB Log (Active)</h3>
        <p>Real-time NinjaBucks transactions for today's session.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card opacity-75">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-icon icon-amber"><i class="bi bi-clipboard-pulse"></i></div>
          <span class="card-badge badge-secondary">NON-FUNCTIONAL</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Progress Log</h3>
        <p>Timestamped history of all rank advancements and changes.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card opacity-75">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-icon icon-amber"><i class="bi bi-folder-fill"></i></div>
          <span class="card-badge badge-secondary">NON-FUNCTIONAL</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Archive Logs</h3>
        <p>Historical transaction records for auditing past sessions.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card opacity-75">
        <div class="card-top">
          <div class="card-icon icon-teal"><i class="bi bi-trophy-fill"></i></div>
          <span class="card-badge badge-secondary">NON-FUNCTIONAL</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Boss Battle</h3>
        <p>Track boss HP, ninja damage dealt, and daily event stats.</p>
        <div class="card-arrow">→</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="boss-card opacity-50">
      <div class="boss-header">
        <span class="boss-title">Today's Boss Battle <span class="badge bg-secondary ms-2" style="font-size: 10px;">NON-FUNCTIONAL</span></span>
        <span class="boss-live">● Live</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hp-label">Boss HP — 62% remaining</div>
      <div class="hp-bar-bg"><div class="hp-bar"></div></div>
      <div class="hp-text"><span>38% damage dealt by ninjas</span><span>Session active</span></div>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>

<script>
  const d = new Date();
  document.getElementById('date-badge').textContent = d.toLocaleDateString('en-CA',{weekday:'short',month:'short',day:'numeric'});
</script>
</body>
</html>
